Jay is happy here.

02:54.862 --> 02:55.724
I don't care.

02:57.517 --> 02:58.379
No, no.

02:59.689 --> 03:00.620
We-

03:01.758 --> 03:03.517
Let me call you back.

03:10.275 --> 03:10.793
- What's going on?

03:14.724 --> 03:15.758
- Deidra wants full
custody of Jay.

03:17.931 --> 03:20.758
[metronome ticking]

03:29.413 --> 03:31.275
- [Tammy] Well?

03:31.275 --> 03:32.862
- She makes a few valid points.

03:33.862 --> 03:35.896
- Pam.

03:35.896 --> 03:37.862
- Looks like she's
completed parenting classes.

03:39.275 --> 03:41.793
Steady job and her own place.

03:41.793 --> 03:43.965
And it's true, you both
have a hectic schedule.

03:45.827 --> 03:46.931
Plus you moved twice
in three years.

03:46.931 --> 03:48.275
- So?

03:48.275 --> 03:49.379
A lot of people have
hectic schedules

03:49.379 --> 03:50.862
and people move, so what?

03:50.862 --> 03:52.827
- It means that Jay had
to change schools twice.

03:55.000 --> 03:56.793
And what I see, she's not
attacking you, Charles.

03:58.689 --> 03:59.758
Her claim is Jay needs a mother.

04:04.344 --> 04:06.000
I can have a petition
filed in with the court

04:06.000 --> 04:06.758
by close of business today.

04:07.827 --> 04:09.448
- No, no courts.

04:09.448 --> 04:12.482
All right, she sent me a
personal letter for a reason.

04:12.482 --> 04:12.758
She's up to something.

04:15.034 --> 04:17.000
The press finds out that there's
a custody battle brewing,

04:17.000 --> 04:20.275
We need other options.

04:20.275 --> 04:23.655
- Charles, you do know
that I don't work for you?

04:23.655 --> 04:24.551
You married my sister.

04:24.551 --> 04:25.655
I'm only trying to help.

04:25.655 --> 04:28.482
- Pam, please.

04:28.482 --> 04:29.000
He's sorry.

04:31.517 --> 04:32.517
- What are our options?

04:34.344 --> 04:34.896
- Reason with her.

04:40.758 --> 04:42.862
[tense music]

04:57.482 --> 04:57.931
- Excuse me.

05:01.034 --> 05:02.896
Excuse me, miss, miss.

05:06.724 --> 05:07.586
Excuse me, miss, excuse me?

05:11.620 --> 05:14.034
Excuse me, miss.

05:14.034 --> 05:15.551
- Deidra, Deidra.
- Excuse me?

05:15.551 --> 05:18.586
- Hello?

05:18.586 --> 05:19.896
[intense noises]

05:19.896 --> 05:22.103
♪You and I you and I

