18:56.517 --> 18:57.689
- So is that why you stopped?

18:59.517 --> 19:00.448
- We both did.

19:02.379 --> 19:05.379
We got married and we tried
to make the family thing work.

19:05.379 --> 19:08.793
He went back to work at a
old manufacturing plant.

19:08.793 --> 19:11.379
I went back to school
and we really tried,

19:11.379 --> 19:15.620
