19:20.965 --> 19:21.931
- Uh, no.

19:24.206 --> 19:27.482
- Just that I'm a crazy
mama that abandoned her kid.

19:28.586 --> 19:30.793
- No, Deidre, he never said any-

19:30.793 --> 19:32.793
- I had so much love
for him, for our family,

19:33.689 --> 19:34.758
until he got arrested.

19:36.310 --> 19:37.620
That was the
beginning of the end.

19:39.275 --> 19:39.793
- Arrested?

19:42.310 --> 19:43.655
- I've said too much.

19:45.620 --> 19:47.482
- No, you haven't said enough.

19:51.275 --> 19:52.655
What was he arrested for?

19:53.793 --> 19:56.620
- Whatever happened
with us is in the past.

19:56.620 --> 19:57.931
He's with you now.

19:57.931 --> 19:59.793
- Yeah, but he never
told me any of this.

20:00.965 --> 20:03.275
- I'm not gonna start any more
trouble than I already have.

20:03.275 --> 20:04.931
He's found his way
back to his music.

20:06.586 --> 20:07.724
He's happy.

20:09.275 --> 20:09.931
You're happy.

20:11.793 --> 20:14.724
[melancholy music]

20:31.793 --> 20:32.620
And Jay's happy.

20:35.965 --> 20:38.448
I had a lawyer draw those
up and I signed them.

20:40.793 --> 20:42.827
I realized that there was
no upside for a waitress

20:42.827 --> 20:45.793
up against a successful
music producer in court.

20:48.620 --> 20:49.482
Take it.

20:53.655 --> 20:56.793
Besides, a custody
battle is no way to start

20:56.793 --> 20:58.551
a healthy co-parenting
relationship.

21:01.517 --> 21:03.344
- Wow, Deidra.

21:03.344 --> 21:03.793
Thank you.

21:06.655 --> 21:07.689
- This was fun.

21:08.827 --> 21:09.655
- It was.

21:09.655 --> 21:10.517
We should do it again.

21:11.896 --> 21:14.896
- Oh, by tomorrow,
you will be so famous

21:14.896 --> 21:17.034
you won't remember that
cheap wine I served you.

21:17.034 --> 21:19.517
- Oh, from me, your
lips to God's ears.

21:20.827 --> 21:22.517
