that cheap, Deidra.

21:24.482 --> 21:27.379
[dog barking]

21:27.379 --> 21:29.517
- That's just Renegade,
the neighbors dog.

21:30.413 --> 21:31.000
It's, he's harmless.

21:32.724 --> 21:33.655
- He don't sound that harmless.

21:33.655 --> 21:34.689
- You get used to it.

21:36.689 --> 21:38.000
[phone beeping]

21:38.000 --> 21:38.724
Oh.

21:41.034 --> 21:42.724
[Deidra giggling]

21:42.724 --> 21:45.034
